{"tid":1277090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(急) 有冇人一樣俾人玩電話？","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T03:21:43.000Z","uid":265974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"511a385cdd130056baaf5310473fa669b5704a43","tid":1277090,"uid":265974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"話說我女朋友都同我一齊有參與幾次遊行<br />\n但就無再參與其他行動<br />\n<br />\n咁女朋友就有屋企人住喺大陸<br />\n佢話今日無啦啦收到大陸屋企人打電話落嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">叫佢唔好去「嗰啲地方」</span><br />\n但問題喺大陸應該封鎖曬消息<br />\n佢屋企人又係網都唔識得上嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到底係有人亂玩電話定點?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7085938404f8ad2035ef00326e5fa9f6dc15cd78","tid":1277090,"uid":162480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"我呢兩日都收到廣東珠海打嚟嘅電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db615dd9ec0d43cd7001671c77abd33f31e01ee5","tid":1277090,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"買張儲蓄卡或者年卡轉下嚟用"}]}